365
00:17:12,534 --> 00:17:15,161
I'm worried too 'cause he's
the best disciple we've got.

366
00:17:15,161 --> 00:17:17,622
Well, technically speaking
he's the only one we've got,

367
00:17:17,622 --> 00:17:19,290
but that's beside the point.

368
00:17:23,706 --> 00:17:26,417
I'm not gonna beat
around the bush here.

369
00:17:26,417 --> 00:17:29,587
I want you to be
part of my crew!

370
00:17:29,587 --> 00:17:31,381
Word on the street is
that Kisara's people

371
00:17:31,381 --> 00:17:33,049
have been causing
you problems lately.

372
00:17:33,049 --> 00:17:36,719
And from what I hear, they're
planning to take you down.

373
00:17:36,719 --> 00:17:38,930
