graduate from high school?

386
00:18:07,792 --> 00:18:09,919
You can't be a delinquent
forever, you know.

387
00:18:09,919 --> 00:18:11,629
Eventually you and all
of your thug friends

388
00:18:11,629 --> 00:18:14,298
are gonna have to grow
up and get real jobs!

389
00:18:25,893 --> 00:18:29,522
Come on Boss, take it easy!
Just calm down, okay?

390
00:18:29,522 --> 00:18:31,524
My men and I don't need
your clever logic!

391
00:18:31,524 --> 00:18:33,568
There's no way you
could ever understand

392
00:18:33,568 --> 00:18:35,695
that a man's greatest desire
in his life is freedom.

393
00:18:35,695 --> 00:18:39,198
Everything that my men
and I do is about being free.

394
00:18:39,198 --> 00:18:41,617
I can understand that, but
if you're harming people

395
00:18:41,617 --> 00:18:43,578
to get your way then
that's not right!

396
00:18:43,578 --> 00:18:45,288
You and your gang are
running around town

397
00:18:45,288 --> 00:18:46,956
enjoying your "freedom" but
all you're really doing

398
00:18:46,956 --> 00:18:48,750
is causing other people pain.

399
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:50,168
