400
00:18:50,168 --> 00:18:52,670
Don't you see?
That's tyranny!

401
00:18:55,548 --> 00:18:57,300
Come on, Boss let's
get out of here!

402
00:18:57,300 --> 00:18:58,843
The little punk's not
worth your trouble!

403
00:18:58,843 --> 00:19:00,678
I don't care what you say.

404
00:19:00,678 --> 00:19:03,056
I'm not gonna join your gang.

405
00:19:03,056 --> 00:19:05,808
