you with words,

411
00:19:17,862 --> 00:19:19,906
I'll just have to fight
you with my fists!

412
00:19:19,906 --> 00:19:22,408
Ever since back in the day,
men have decided who was right

413
00:19:22,408 --> 00:19:23,993
by settling their disagreements
with a fight.

414
00:19:23,993 --> 00:19:25,870
You don't have any
problems with that do you?

415
00:19:25,870 --> 00:19:27,705
You know, it's
guys like this tool

416
00:19:27,705 --> 00:19:30,124
